Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and happiness, and anything else is\Nfacious. Um
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.96,0:19:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,there's probably some other way we're\Ngoing to be able to uh
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,uh substitute for people who are not\Nthemselves adept at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you uh handle people that are in\Nyour life that are non-intigorous?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh well, Jesus said to avoid them.\Nuh you join any serious spiritual order,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.67,0:19:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,they're going to tell you you're going\Nto have to leave them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.44,0:19:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh what if you have to work with them?\NIf you have to work with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,then you are coming from a certain\Nspecific role, a certain archetype.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're coming from the healer.\NThat's different
