Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.64,0:20:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,test them out between before kinesiology\Nbefore I even call them back and
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,uh\Nit's just it's an unwillingness on my
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,part anymore to deal with what I've\Ndealt with for so many years
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's just a personal choice\Nbut that's exactly what we do. We check
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,them out. So and so wants his\Nappointment. I check him out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.03,0:20:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Okay. I don't ask why. I just assume\Nthat God's will for me is that this is
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,not the kind of person that I should\Nprobably spend time with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:21:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh\Nthese various states of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,are we are there are their own reality.\NThey are their own reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,on an experiential basis.\NThe experience of hell is extremely
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,hellish.\NThese are all different levels of
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.60,0:21:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness.\NEach one is valid within its own domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one is valid within itself.\Nthe teachings of all the great teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.03,0:21:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what Jesus taught was\Navoid anything that calibrates below
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,200. That's all he said,\Nright? That's all he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And traditionally, it's called sin.\NBut it really is just everything under
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.36,0:21:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,200. Greed, avarice, malice, hatred,\Nall these things. He said avoid all that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.03,0:22:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,because if you hang out in it when you\Nleave the body you will go to the realm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.20,0:22:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that calibrates at that level.\NYou will go to the realm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.36,0:22:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,like a cork in water is the way I said.\NYou don't have to worry about what
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.55,0:22:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,happens to your soul, at least the body,\Nbecause it's like a cork in water. And
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.20,0:22:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the absolute justice of all\Nof creation, it will automatically
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,gravitate to that to which it is\Naligned.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.32,0:22:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It will automatically gravitate to that\Nwhich is aligned. There is nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.32,0:22:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,arbitrary going on in the universe. Huh?\NThere's nothing arbitrary.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The justice of God is absolute,\Ninfinite, and impeccable. Each thing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.79,0:22:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,only experiences\Nout of its own
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual decisions that which it has\Nchosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.67,0:23:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Having experienced that, it may change\Nits mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.40,0:23:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and how\Nin the pit of hell I said
