Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.55,0:23:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,anythingness\Nwas removed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.20,0:23:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,when you see that hell goes on for\Neternity forever without any possibility
