Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.24,0:23:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There goes your last\Ncard of this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.96,0:23:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he took that before you said if\Nthere is a god I ask him to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.48,0:24:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And then to the opposite end of the\Nspectrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.15,0:24:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So each is its reality on its own level.\NThe spectacular presence, the infinite
